<paragraph id="729A77E879FBC8AEEE190720EF07312E" pageId="0" pageNumber="62878">
TENERIFE: Granadilla de Abona, El 
<normalizedToken id="A78ACD3CC7F1AA8E3C62409326D3814E" originalValue="Médano">Medano</normalizedToken>
, beach, barranco de los Calderones, from sewage sludge, a single individual, 14.11.2016, 
<emphasis id="5387478F279D7BAC068EBF85442B3DB6" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="62878">F. Verloove</emphasis>
